SUBJECT_CREATE_USER="Welcome to LMS - Your Library Adventure Begins!"

TEXT_CREATE_USER=`Dear ${req.body.name},

We are thrilled to welcome you to LMS, your gateway to a world of knowledge and imagination! Thank you for creating an account with us, and congratulations on taking the first step to explore a vast collection of books and resources.

At LMS, we are committed to providing you with a seamless and enriching library experience. As a registered member, you now have access to a plethora of features that will make your library journey truly enjoyable. Here are some key highlights:

Search and Discover: Our advanced search functionality allows you to explore our extensive library catalog effortlessly. Whether you're looking for classic novels, academic journals, or the latest bestsellers, you'll find them all at your fingertips.

Borrow and Renew: With just a few clicks, you can borrow books and other materials and even renew them if you need more time to delve into their pages. We want to make sure you have ample opportunity to explore every captivating story.

Personalized Recommendations: Our intelligent recommendation system will suggest books based on your interests and reading history, introducing you to new authors and genres you might love.

Stay Connected: Be the first to know about exciting library events, workshops, and book clubs through our regular email updates. Engage with fellow book enthusiasts and be part of our vibrant community.

Easy Access Anywhere: Take your reading with you wherever you go! Our responsive website design ensures that you can access the library from any device, be it your computer, tablet, or smartphone.

Library Resources Online: For those who prefer digital resources, we offer a growing collection of e-books, audiobooks, and other electronic materials for your convenience.

If you ever need assistance or have any questions, our dedicated team of librarians is here to help. Feel free to reach out to us through our contact page, and we'll be more than happy to assist you.

Once again, welcome to LMS. We hope your journey with us will be filled with delightful discoveries and endless inspiration. Happy reading!

Best regards,
The LMS Team`


